	measure 'Market Value Quarter Change In %' = ```
			
			VAR CY = [Market Value]
			VAR PY = 
			    CALCULATE(
			        [Market Value],
			        OFFSET(
			            -1,
			            ALL('Date'[Year Quarter Name]),
			            ORDERBY( 'Date'[Year Quarter Name], ASC)
			        )
			    )
			VAR _perc = DIVIDE( CY-PY, PY )
			VAR _format = FORMAT( _perc, "0.00 %;0.00 %" )
			RETURN
			IF(
			    ISBLANK(PY),
			    "",
			    IF(
			        _perc > 0,
			        _format & " " & UNICHAR(129029),
			        IF(
			            _perc < 0,
			            _format & "  " & UNICHAR(129031),
			            _format & "  " & UNICHAR(129030)
			        )
			    )
			)
			```
		displayFolder: Performance
		lineageTag: 05d45fb7-b955-4c27-9d99-d90b359f81ee

		changedProperty = IsHidden

